Interface IOptional<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IScriptingObject, Iterable<T>

    public interface IOptional<T>
extends Iterable<T>, IScriptingObject
    This type is mimics regular java Optional but adds a few methods/functionality for backwards compatibility.
